IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: TO PROVIDE HANDICAPPED PERSONS WITH HOUSING FACILITIES AND SERVICES SPECIALLY DESIGNED TO MEET THEIR PHYSICAL, SOCIAL, AND PSYCHOLOICAL NEEDS AND TO PROMOTE THEIR HEALTH, SECURITY, HAPPINESS AND USEFULNESS IN LONGER LIVING.
IRS990.MissionDesc: VOLUNTEERS OF AMERICA OF FLORIDA, INC. (VOAFL) (AND AFFILIATES) IS A NONPROFIT SPIRITUALLY BASED HUMAN SERVICES ORGANIZATION, INCORPORATED IN THE STATE OF FLORIDA, THAT PROVIDES SOCIAL SERVICES WITHIN THE STATE UNDER A CHARTER FROM VOLUNTEERS OF AMERICA, INC. (VOA, INC.) A NATIONAL NONPROFIT SPIRITUALLY BASED ORGANIZATION PROVIDING LOCAL HUMAN SERVICE PROGRAMS AND OPPORTUNITIES FOR INDIVIDUAL AND COMMUNITY INVOLVEMENT, TO HELP MENTALLY ILL AND HOMELESS INDIVIDUALS BECOME STRONG WITHIN SOCIETY AND TO HELP VETERANS WITH HOMELESSNESS ISSUES ALONG WITH EDUCATION TO IMPROVE CURRENT LIVING STANDARDS.
IRS990.Desc: TO FOSTER INDEPENDENCE AND PROVIDE AFFORDABLE HOUSING PROVIDED FOR PHYSICALLY AND MENTALLY HANDICAPPED INDIVIDUALS.
